gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 126, Magic 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Magic, 126-99. Sam Merrill recorded 26 points (8-13 3PM) and three rebounds for the Cavaliers, with Donovan Mitchell adding 25 points, 13 assists, and three rebounds in the victory. Paolo Banchero tallied 18 points, six assists, and three rebounds for the Magic in the losing effort. The Cavaliers improve to 26-15, while the Magic fall to 23-21.
